## GitHub Linguist ##
# Show the repo as gameplay code first, not imported Unity asset packs
Assets/Scripts/** linguist-detectable=true
*.cs linguist-language=C#

# Ignore Unity serialized assets from language stats
*.shader linguist-detectable=false
*.cginc linguist-detectable=false
*.mat linguist-detectable=false
*.prefab linguist-detectable=false
*.unity linguist-detectable=false
*.asset linguist-detectable=false
*.meta linguist-detectable=false
*.controller linguist-detectable=false
*.anim linguist-detectable=false

# Ignore imported/vendor asset packs from GitHub language breakdown
Assets/PolyAnarchy/** linguist-vendored
Assets/BreakableAsteroids/** linguist-vendored
Assets/BlackHole/** linguist-vendored
Assets/TextMesh Pro/** linguist-vendored
Assets/Sci-FiSpaceFighterPBR/** linguist-vendored
Assets/Free Skyboxes - Space/** linguist-vendored
Assets/SpaceSkies Free/** linguist-vendored

# Ignore docs/web build output from language stats
docs/** linguist-generated
